\pard\sa200 This revision addresses review comments against v0.13. It keeps the architecture buildable while tightening terminology and removing ambiguous wording. In particular, it restores the simple addition model for effective weights, renames gradient symbols to grad_effective style, defines gradient_projector before use, replaces covered with remainder-enabled, groups R0/R1/R2 into one optimiser section, and makes DDP compatibility a hard requirement.\par
